    <h2 class="section__title">Typography</h2>

      <p class="section__text">There are several global (un-namespaced) styles. These are: all <b>typographic elements</b>, <b>body</b>, and <b>links</b>. Font sizes are set for all typographic elements globally.</p>

    <p class="section__text">
      The root <code>&lt;html&gt;</code> element is set at:
