    <p class="section__text">
      The <code>&lt;body&gt;</code> element uses the <b>Libre Franklin</b> font, consistent with <a href="" target="_blank">UT guidelines</a>.
    </p>

    <pre><code>body { font-family: 'Libre Franklin', sans-serif; }</code></pre>

    <p class="section__text">Headings and <code>&lt;p&gt;</code> elements also have specified color and font weight:</p>
    <pre><code>h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {
    font-family: 'Libre Franklin', sans-serif;
    color: #404040;
    font-weight: 700;
}
p, li {
    font-size: 1em;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1.6em;
    color: #333;
}</code></pre>
